stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> New
    New --> InReview: Analyst opens incident
    InReview --> Escalated: Needs deeper review
    InReview --> Contained: Immediate action taken
    InReview --> Closed: Benign or resolved
    InReview --> FalsePositive: Approved activity
    Escalated --> Contained: Response action
    Escalated --> Closed: Resolution confirmed
    Contained --> Closed: Recovery complete
